This is the quintessential Genovese basil, perfected for the modern urban garden through generations of selective breeding. Mini-Sweet Basil 4.1 delivers the full, sweet, and complexly aromatic flavour of its heirloom ancestors in a compact, prolific form that thrives on frequent harvesting, making it the ultimate living ingredient for your kitchen.

